1
00:00:02,840 --> 00:00:04,130
Hinata.

2
00:00:06,340 --> 00:00:10,970
Waiting for you to come home
is actually really nice.

3
00:00:11,470 --> 00:00:15,600
Thinking of you coming home exhausted
and eating the meals I cooked,

4
00:00:15,600 --> 00:00:20,400
scarfing it down and saying "It's delicious"
just makes me smile.

5
00:00:21,520 --> 00:00:23,110
Really?

6
00:00:23,110 --> 00:00:24,360
Yeah.

7
00:00:44,960 --> 00:00:46,760
I love you.

8
00:00:48,630 --> 00:00:50,090
I love you too.
